      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"DragonCompositing-Compositing\">Compositing</h3><p>Thankfully, the render came out of RenderMan very nicely, and it didn't need much fixing in compositing. I decided to use Photoshop because I've used it for a long time and I’m pretty comfortable with it.</p><p>The background is a simple soft gradient, with adjusted light and shadow contrasts on the dragon. I also increased the brightness in a few areas and did some post-processing. After a minimal touch of color grading … voila!</p><p /><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Tip 1: Keep it simple … less is more.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Tip 2: Keep the original image to compare it with your changes.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Tip 3: Don't over sharpen your image, as it kills realism. Like saturation, this is an effect that people like to exaggerate to the detriment of their image, as a real lens is not as sharp as a computer generated image.</p>\n</div></div><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"sorindar-final.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621227/sorindar-final.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591803205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=912\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657621227/sorindar-final.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591803205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"2400\" data-width=\"2000\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657391735\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"sorindar-final.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657621227\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d9d7054d-b04f-423a-a304-999071c9a155\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621227/sorindar-final.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591803205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=1824 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657621227/sorindar-final.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762591803205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=912 1x\"></span><hr/>"
